\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/celsonatale\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4ef0fb07eb70517f15b87417eea60a4f?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/4ef0fb07eb70517f15b87417eea60a4f?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/celsonatale\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">abcelso <small>(celsonatale)<\/small><\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">April 15, 2022<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Que plugin sensacional!! Muito bem constru\u00eddo, simples de configurar, leve, funciona perfeitamente e a customiza\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 na medida exata, permitindo que altere as principais express\u00f5es exibidas para o usu\u00e1rio. Al\u00e9m de tudo, democratiza o acesso ao Pix para lojas virtuais pequenas que usam o Woocommerce.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Muito Bom<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/giovanebertol\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/69f7f78d4f9d450a418511ab6347a1b7?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/69f7f78d4f